---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Videos | Motunrayo Koyejo" 
  currentPage="videos"
>
  <header style="padding: 80px 0 20px;">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="eyebrow">Videos</div>
      <h1>Tech, but make it <em>human</em>.</h1>
      <p class="lede">Somewhere between "stop being so jargon-y" and "I genuinely wish someone had explained this to me earlier," I started making videos. They live on YouTube and TikTok, and they're mostly about software engineering, fintech, and career navigation.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section style="padding: 20px 0;">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="cta-band" style="margin-top: 0;">
        <h3>Come hang out.</h3>
        <p>New videos land most weeks. Subscribe on YouTube if you like things explained properly, follow on TikTok if you like things explained in sixty seconds.</p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <a class="cta-btn" href="https://www.youtube.com/@motunrayokoyejo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Subscribe on YouTube ↗</a>
          <a class="cta-btn" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@motushbae" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="background: transparent; color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid var(--accent);">Follow on TikTok ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>